FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about making the Goods
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: 'The Goods' refer to high-quality, handcrafted products made with care and expertise using our app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the app help me make the Goods?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our app provides step-by-step guides, video tutorials, and a supportive community to help you create top-notch goods with ease.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Do I need prior experience to use this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: No prior experience is necessary. Our app caters to beginners and experts alike, offering resources for all skill levels.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I sell the Goods I make using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! We encourage users to monetize their creations. The app even includes tips on marketing and selling your goods.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a cost to use the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a free basic version with essential features. For advanced tools and exclusive content, we have affordable premium plans available.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Making the Goods
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: 'The Goods' refer to high-quality, handcrafted products that are made with care and attention to detail. Our app helps you create these premium items with ease.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does this app help me make the Goods?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app provides step-by-step guides, video tutorials, and a supportive community to help you master the art of making the Goods. From selecting materials to perfecting techniques, we've got you covered.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Do I need prior experience to use this app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Not at all! Whether you're a beginner or an experienced craftsperson, our app caters to all skill levels. We offer projects ranging from simple to advanced, allowing you to progress at your own pace.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I sell the Goods I make using this app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! We encourage users to turn their passion into profit. Our app includes tips on marketing and selling your creations, as well as a marketplace feature where you can showcase and sell your Goods to other app users.
